PrecisApproval of the reappointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JACQUES BRUNELLE, of Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective June 16, 2001.
